parsePreferredLocales

protected static com.nimbusds.langtag.LangTag[] parsePreferredLocales(net.minidev.json.JSONObject object)
                                                               throws com.nimbusds.langtag.LangTagException
Parses a preferred locales array, by order of preference.

Parameters:
object - The JSON object to parse, any locales must be specified as language tags (RFC 5646) in a JSON array named "preferred_locales".
Returns:
The preferred locales array, null if not specified.
Throws:
com.nimbusds.langtag.LangTagException - If an invalid language tag is encountered.
